l students during a period of considerable change in the legal profession has been a good life i have also enjoyed scholarship especially work on the life of a pioneer in the law who conceived the idea of the public defender woman lawyer the trials of clara foltz is forthcoming this year from the stanford press i have been married to fellow stanford law professor tom grey for more than thirty years he too has retired and spends his creative energy on bird photography now here is a picture of us at a farmer's market with our grandchild dinah grey luomanen 7 comments are closed search for woman lawyer the trials of clara foltz order information available at stanford press amazon com follow clara foltz on facebook 2012 women's legal history
